videos.description: Texas takes an 8-point lead into halftime after Joanne Allen-Taylor beats the shot clock buzzer late in the second quarter.

videos.description: NaLyssa Smith and Queen Egbo each score go-ahead buckets for Baylor in the third quarter vs. Texas.

videos.description: Before the shot clock expires, Ja'Mee Asberry throws up a 3-pointer from well beyond the arc and gets it to go for Baylor.

videos.description: Queen Egbo grabs a rebound and sends a long pass to NaLyssa Smith, who scores to increase Baylor's lead over Texas.
